{
  "schema": "url-probe-scenarios.v1",
  "description": "Slice 487 §3.1 — URL-emission probe scenarios against the live JustSearch OperationCatalog + CoreSurfaceCatalog (rendered 2026-05-12 from a backend with 27 ops + 9 surfaces). Each scenario gives Qwen3.5-9B a prompt and an expectedURL; the url-emitter system prompt carries the catalog grammar.",
  "notes": [
    "Op ids are dot-separated (`core.bulk-reindex`); surface ids end with `-surface` (`core.library-surface`).",
    "All scenarios run on the `url-emitter` profile (toolSubset: []); the model emits plain text with URLs.",
    "Categories: nav-* (surface navigation), op-* (single operation), multi-* (≥2 URLs), phrasing-* (robustness), query-* (548 S4-A free-text search verb justsearch://query?q=...)."
  ],
  "systemPromptPath": "url-probe-system-prompt.md",
